{"tid":2458043,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"豹哥陳蕾係咪暗黃？","createTime":"2021-03-23T06:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T06:27:02.000Z","uid":247211,"like":3,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3f71dff382ebd46cd3a1c1d53828f3c3779234ed","tid":2458043,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mb708YYAxFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMb708YYAxFc&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97RAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=1c7ea40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mb708YYAxFc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHyO2BL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHyO2BL.jpg&h=13b79f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n僆儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMeOh95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMeOh95.jpg&h=0d98e7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保鮮紙包手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjvNyJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjvNyJq.jpg&h=346657ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眼罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPmQwu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPmQwu5.jpg&h=6e9ffc7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇埋歌詞<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美女變了隻七面獸</span> ＝》14年佔中暗角打獲七黑警<br />\n隨歪風去擺柳<br />\n<span class=\"red\">壯漢也變了機械獸</span> ＝》本來深得人心既警隊變成冇腦只收order做野既機械獸<br />\n隨便踐踏蟻丘<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">現今劊子手 哪需一刀在手</span> ＝》劊子手 = 黑警 &amp; 狗官，武器 = 法律<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有戲法就會批鬥</span> ＝》你得民心就會被批鬥<br />\n<br />\n困進這裡化身異獸<br />\n純真都變污垢<br />\n有血有性卻卑賤過<br />\n<span class=\"red\">橫巷的那隻狗</span> ＝》成段都係講黑警<br />\n<br />\n或者回回頭 有妖怪在背後<br />\n隨時可拐帶擄走 ＝》之前好多手足被消失<br />\n<br />\n誰亦張口舞爪 不分美醜<br />\n半點骨氣怎去守<br />\n還是烏煙四周 更是時候<br />\n<span class=\"red\">以風骨應對這荒謬</span> ＝》香港人剩返良知風骨堅持<br />\n<span class=\"red\">妖治時代</span> 街上全是很妖冶的色誘 ＝》支那中共<br />\n心水清得通透<br />\n不怕赤手 鬼也嚇走<br />\nBa La Ba Ba<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">過去錯信了豬隊友</span> ＝》信錯泛民大中華膠<br />\n神經都快失救<br />\n<span class=\"red\">似隻豹卻至可敵對</span> ＝》勇武先係出路<br />\n神一般那對手<br />\n<br />\n自知而頑強 帶青澀在眼眸<br />\n就令小丑也顫抖<br />\n<br />\n獵物逐一倒了 神仙都也發燒<br />\n<span class=\"red\">望望有幾多個 連羞恥也拋掉</span> ＝》支共派議員<br />\n大鱷在陰陰笑 想勇士折腰<br />\n或是捍衛純白 更是微妙<br />\n才能跟妖怪鬥妖<br />\n<br />\n還未生出百足 長出尾巴<br />\n最真本性總要守<br />\n牛或馬在狂號 繼續崇尚<br />\n<span class=\"red\">人暴烈仍帶種溫柔</span> ＝》勇武但不失溫柔<br />\n崩壞年代 不用臣服於妖獸的詛咒<br />\n不中伏就自由<br />\n不會發嬲 不會錯手<br />\n心傲氣高 便成高手<br />\n不怕赤手 鬼也嚇走<br />\nBa La Ba Ba<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豹哥陳蕾係咪暗黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ccacf9cf19eb5508e9bb7536e70d329fde52d9","tid":2458043,"uid":247211,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"［多圖警世］渣打銀行Kenny Yip借文宣acc騷擾女手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gMePMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gMePMS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>kenny yip你咪撚諗住抄post</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3e61e5ae7847b31055806cd2460c9dce6bbd8c07","tid":2458043,"uid":191385,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b751f662210674199d0babacd06bded531aedf57","tid":2458043,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislik